short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides autocomplete suggestions for appliance model numbers

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: If you take service calls or perform triage and prescreening in the appliance industry, you know the frustration of midheard and mistyped model numbers when reviewing customer work orders. This uses a looser search to provide suggestions that may be correct, then you can click to copy to your clipboard and paste in your appliance parts distributor's site for accurate parts information.
